snippet.title: A Few Thoughts on Troublesome Zero (Tanton Mathematics)
snippet.description: The concept of zero is hard! And if you really think about it, the mathematics of zero is also hard! Here is a quick overview of some troubles with troublesome zero. (Can we help our students?)
